        <p class="hero-eyebrow">Clean Caffeine. From Green Tea.</p>
        <p>Caffeine is the world's most familiar nootropic. The science is direct: it blocks adenosine, the molecule that builds up through the day and signals fatigue. Less adenosine signal, more alertness.</p>
        <p>Not all caffeine is the same. Most energy drinks and pre-workouts use synthetic caffeine, the cheapest form. DayShift uses caffeine from green tea leaf extract, naturally paired with antioxidants like EGCG and gentler on the stomach than coffee.</p>
      </div>
